sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as Express API
    participant Cache
    participant Master as MySQL Master
    participant Replica as MySQL Replica

    Client->>API: POST /api/products<br/>{product data}

    Note over API: Route to Master<br/>for Write Operation

    API->>Master: INSERT INTO products
    Master-->>API: Success (ID: 101)

    Note over API,Replica: Simulate Replication Lag

    API->>API: setTimeout(2000ms)
    API-->>Client: 201 Created<br/>{productId: 101, replicationDelay: 2000ms}

    Note over API: Clear Cache<br/>Pattern: /products

    API->>Cache: clearCache('/products')
    Cache-->>API: Cache cleared

    Note over API,Replica: After 2000ms delay

    API->>Replica: INSERT INTO products
    Replica-->>API: Replication complete

    Note over Master,Replica: Databases now in sync
